{"tid":2054553,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社民連 到 美領 抗議警暴：「香港人民都要聲援美國嘅人民！」","createTime":"2020-06-07T08:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T15:50:35.000Z","uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cb0b800cf60d8c947a012efdee65d0ac18c5a469","tid":2054553,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:57:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/社民連赴美領館示威-聲援-black-lives-matter-警再以限聚令阻攔/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%B0%91%E9%80%A3%E8%B5%B4%E7%BE%8E%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4-black-lives-matter-%E8%AD%A6%E5%86%8D%E4%BB%A5%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E9%98%BB%E6%94%94%2F&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=c82adb16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%B0%91%E9%80%A3%E8%B5%B4%E7%BE%8E%E9%A0%98%E9%A4%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E8%81%B2%E6%8F%B4-black-lives-matter-%E8%AD%A6%E5%86%8D%E4%BB%A5%E9%99%90%E8%81%9A%E4%BB%A4%E9%98%BB%E6%94%94%2F&h=8c93cb11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/社民連赴美領館示威-聲援-black-lives-matter-警再以限聚令阻攔/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/101868026_10220572072084199_1414505176825037130_o_welnj_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F101868026_10220572072084199_1414505176825037130_o_welnj_1200x0.png&h=28c9782a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n社民連今日聯同一批居港外藉人士到美國領事館請願，聲緩美國「Black Lives Matter」運動，他們高呼「No justice, no peace（沒有公義，哪有和平）」、「Stop police brutality （反對警察暴力）」口號。十多名參與人士前往美國領事館期間，一度被警方以「限聚令」為由攔截，只能以每次 8 人的流水方式示威。社民連梁國雄說，附近有大群外傭聚集，而且他們距離相近，但警方亦未有理會，批評警方是針對政治表達執法。<br />\n<br />\n社民連吳文遠說，美國的情況與香港相似，都是起初以和平的方式抗議，但因為面對警暴問題，而引發更激烈的示威活動，認為「美國一路睇住香港人嘅抗爭，一路支持緊嘅時候，香港人民都要聲援美國嘅人民」。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，早前有網民自發組織聲援美國示威的行動，唯與警方聯絡後，因「限聚令」而未能獲發不反對通知書，活動被逼宣佈取消。不過今日仍有十多名居港外藉人士按呼籲到中環遮打花園集合，社民連代他們與警方交涉，警方堅持只容許 8 人前往美國領事館，活動最後需每次 8 個人輪流示威，他形容這是無奈的做法。"},{"pid":"4c60a50fb7d083c7469159e80dd47b39e25c9739","tid":2054553,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee88120e7ada052bd22ba4b94ba1bae818d80cf","tid":2054553,"uid":314204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"10f41e8d62939aec359a75ec9d24488a319abd77","tid":2054553,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:07:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5245ea8b0bd2a3b8d5145462e2d2bc18cefc2b0c","tid":2054553,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:11:05.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"54e41563061d9cd7fcbaee52e32e94bf2acb4882","tid":2054553,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:11:37.000Z","msg":"個運動一早畀人騎劫咗啦"},{"pid":"abab7772fb665380a18fe5da0151aa12276394c7","tid":2054553,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"Okay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff4c0a9030e9d45e62e3f9a5cbd8d06c7c6cf0d7","tid":2054553,"uid":77180,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:20:07.000Z","msg":"社民連不代表我"},{"pid":"e55044700683c19653552ff4af33e3b2117c0f38","tid":2054553,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"ON撚9"},{"pid":"ba661a7755beacca9b1921567dbaa068d94f1920","tid":2054553,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T09:40:44.000Z","msg":"香港都未追究到去理人地國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7c1363301fefd8d6e97b2ff9654a0b4d64d1bb","tid":2054553,"uid":326725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:50:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkRCYc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkkRCYc1.png&h=f49e9582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}